 Stability AI 发布 Stable Code 3B 以增强编码辅助https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/2024/01/17/stability-ai-releases-stable-code-3b-enhanced-coding-assistance/ https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/2024/01/17/stability-ai-releases-stable-code-3b-enhanced-coding-assistance/#respondRyan Daws Wed, 17 Jan 2024 12:15:11 +0000 ApplicationsArtificial Intelligenceaiartificial intelligencecode generationcodingprogrammingsoftware developmentstability aistable codestable code 3b https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/?p=14183 <p> Stability AI 宣布发布 Stable Code 3B，这是一个升级后的 30 亿参数人工智能系统，用于自动代码生成和完成。通过更大的上下文大小和更高的完成质量等增强功能，Stable Code 3B 旨在突破人工智能辅助软件开发的界限。 Stable Code 3B 的设计仅包含 30 亿个参数<a class="excerpt-read-more" href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/2024/01/17/stability-ai-releases-stable-code-3b-enhanced-coding-assistance/" title="ReadStability AI 发布稳定代码 3B 以增强编码帮助">... 阅读更多 ”</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/2024/01/17/stability-ai-releases-stable-code-3b-enhanced-coding-assistance/">Stability AI 发布稳定代码 3B 以增强编码帮助后</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com">AI News</a>上。</p> ; 
<p><a href="https://stability.ai/">Stability AI</a>宣布发布<a href="https://huggingface.co/stabilityai/stable-code-3b">Stable Code 3B</a> ，这是一个升级后的 30 亿参数人工智能系统，用于自动代码生成和完成。</p><p>通过更大的上下文大小和更高的完成质量等增强功能，Stable Code 3B 旨在突破人工智能辅助软件开发的界限。</p><p> Stable Code 3B 仅有 30 亿个参数，旨在在笔记本电脑等现成硬件上高效运行，这与需要昂贵的专用芯片的大型模型不同。尽管其尺寸较小，但该公司声称其代码完成质量可达到或超过其尺寸两倍以上的模型。</p><p>该系统建立在 Stability AI 的 Stable LM 自然语言模型的基础上，并针对代码存储库和程序员论坛等软件工程数据进行了额外的培训。它涵盖了Python、JavaScript、Java、C++和Go等18种编程语言。</p><p>该模型的训练过程通过结合旋转位置嵌入 (RoPE) 进行了优化，扩大了上下文大小以提高性能。 Meta 的 Llama 2 Long 也采用了这项技术，允许上下文长度高达 100k 标记。</p><p>除了简单地建议新的代码行之外，它还可以填充现有代码中大量缺失的部分。这种高级功能称为“中间填充”(FIM)，允许它自动编写整个函数或组件。</p><p>人工智能生成代码领域引起了微软、OpenAI 和 Meta 等科技巨头的浓厚兴趣。 Stability AI 的新系统优于 StarCoder 等同类模型，并使其成为这个快速发展领域的领导者： </p><figure class="wp-block-image size-large"><img decoding="async" width="1024" height="360" src="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/stability-ai-stable-code-3b-benchmarks-1024x360.png" alt="" class="wp-image-14184" srcset="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/stability-ai-stable-code-3b-benchmarks-1024x360.png 1024w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/stability-ai-stable-code-3b-benchmarks-300x106.png 300w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/stability-ai-stable-code-3b-benchmarks-768x270.png 768w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/stability-ai-stable-code-3b-benchmarks-1536x541.png 1536w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/stability-ai-stable-code-3b-benchmarks-380x134.png 380w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/stability-ai-stable-code-3b-benchmarks-350x123.png 350w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/stability-ai-stable-code-3b-benchmarks-100x35.png 100w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/stability-ai-stable-code-3b-benchmarks-60x21.png 60w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2024/01/stability-ai-stable-code-3b-benchmarks.png 1716w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure><p>凭借令人印象深刻的基准测试和高效规模提高的可访问性，Stable Code 3B 旨在为更广泛的受众带来增强的 AI 代码完成功能。它的到来有望进一步加速将生成式人工智能集成到各行业的软件开发工作流程中。</p><p>借助 Stable Code 3B 等自动执行死记硬背编码任务的系统，开发人员将变得更加高效、富有创造力，并且可以将精力集中在更复杂的挑战上。</p><p> <em>（ <a href="https://unsplash.com/@gamell?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">琼·加梅尔</a>在<a href="https://unsplash.com/photos/black-flat-screen-computer-monitor-ZS67i1HLllo?utm_content=creditCopyText&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_source=unsplash">Unsplash</a>上拍摄）</em></p><p><strong>另请参阅：</strong> <a href="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/2024/01/15/imf-ai-could-boost-growth-but-worsen-inequality/"><strong>国际货币基金组织：人工智能可以促进增长，但会加剧不平等</strong></a></p><figure class="wp-block-image size-full"><a href="https://www.ai-expo.net/"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="728" height="90" src="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01.png" alt="" class="wp-image-11874" srcset="https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01.png 728w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01-300x37.png 300w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01-380x47.png 380w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01-350x43.png 350w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01-100x12.png 100w, https://www.artificialintelligence-news.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/9/2022/04/ai-expo-world-728x-90-01-60x7.png 60w" sizes="(max-